$interpreted: Yan-Bo: Returned, Karnulla has not. Pick fruit, is all he has to do. This time, why does it take him so long? Danger, has he met?
Hestia: Yan-Bo〜〜
Yan-Bo: Hestia, the matter, what be?
Hestia:  A platypus is dead and all the other platypuses think it was Karnulla who did it!
Yan-Bo: What! Take me there, you must!
Yan-Bo: Calm down... situation, what is right now?
Platypus: Qua kekekek!
Hestia: They said that the teeth marks on the corpse are those of a frogodile. The only one around here is Karnulla......
Yan-Bo: This cannot be. This sort of thing, Karnulla would not do.
Platypus: Qua kekekek!
Hestia: They said that we'll only know by confronting Karnulla directly!
Yan-Bo: Karnulla......Picking fruit, he is. Returned, he has not.
Hestia: What a coincidence! No proof of absence too. That's more than enough reason for me!
Yan-Bo: Hestia, Karnulla, you do not trust?
Hestia: He's a frogodile! He bites creatures to death and eats them. It's just a matter of time. That's his nature after all!
Yan-Bo: No, no......
Platypus: Kekekek!
Hestia: Wait, wait. This has nothing to do with Yan-Bo. Don't be like this!
Karnulla: How dare you attack Grandpa Yan-Bo!? Are you tired of living? I'll teach you scumbags a lesson!
Yan-Bo: Karnulla, speak like this, you must not!
Yan-Bo: Innocent in this matter, Karnulla is, I believe.
Yan-Bo: The culprit, I shall find. During this time, at home Karnulla will stay. Suspicion, this will prevent.
Karnulla: What? I don't even know what is going on! Why are you locking me inside the house!?
Yan-Bo: Speak no more. Home, we shall return.
Yan-Bo: With anger, you reacted back there. Teach you this, have I? Meditate here, you shall. Think this over, you ought.
Karnulla: .........
Karnulla: Grandpa Yan-Bo, do you really believe that I am innocent?
Yan-Bo: Certainly.
Karnulla: Then what is the reason for grounding me?
Yan-Bo: Prevent more confusion, this will. Sorry to do this to you, I am.
Yan-Bo: A good child, I know you are. Clear you of any suspicion, I shall. Accept you, Hestia and the others will.
Karnulla: ... Understood...
